Subject: [PATCH 01/14] clk: sunxi: Add dummy fixed rate clock for Allwinner
 A1X SoCs

Signed-off-by: Maxime Ripard <maxime.ripard@free-electrons.com>
Cc: Mike Turquette <mturquette@ti.com>
